The,Avasaram,RESTful,Web,Services,API,helps,applications,and,websites,to,communicate,with,Avasaram,platform,The,platform,provides,financial,services,to,help,option,traders,find,opportunities,in,different,markets,The,services,provide,via,API,are,the,Screener,Service,Custom,Screener,Service,Option,Calculator,Service,Vertical,Spread,Calculator,Service,and,the,Analyzer,Service,Developers,can,integrate,the,API,into,their,applications,to,take,advantage,of,the,services,available,on,the,platform